About Me

Hi my name is Ashton and I am a Street, City/Landscape Photographer. 

Ever since I got my first camera in the winter of 2012, I have been hooked. Photography for me is an escape from the real world and is a gateway to be creative and explore. Photography is a challenge that requires planning, location scouting, angles, but most of all patience.

As I grow in photography, it has been rewarding socially as well. I have met so many people that I now calls my friends. This is why I love photography: because of the challenges and the social aspect but, most of all, the freedom of expressing your creativity.

I have a Saying:

"Freezing That Moment FOREVER!"

I take that to heart!

Ashton Tekno.
